-- RC Partners Buys German Solar Park for Institutional Investor
-- B y   S t e f a n   N i c o l a
-- 2013-03-20T16:28:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-20/rc-partners-buys-german-solar-park-for-institutional-investor.html
Renewable Energy Capital Partners
GmbH, a clean-energy investor, bought a 31.5-megawatt solar
plant in  Germany  on behalf of an institutional investor it
didn’t identify. Terms weren’t disclosed.  RC Partners, based in Frankfurt, bought the Flughafen Barth
photovoltaic plant in Mecklenburg Western-Pomerania from RENERCO
Renewable Energy Concepts AG, it said today in an e-mailed
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stefan Nicola in Berlin at 
